    • applyOperation

      public static java.lang.String applyOperation​(MinPriorityQueue<?,​?> pq, java.lang.String before, java.lang.String operation, java.lang.Runnable operations, java.lang.String expected, java.lang.String filename)
      Run a specified series of operations on a PQ and track results.
      Parameters:
      pq - PQ on which to run operations
      before - String representation of heap state before the operation
      operation - String representation of operation
      operations - list of operations
      expected - String representation of expected heap state after operation
      filename - file to which output is written
      Returns:
      String representing final PQ on success, null on failure
